name: {Mumma Necklace} Tuggable. Chewable. Fashionable.
description:
Made with acrylic beads on a double strand of nylon coated stainless steel, double crimped and threaded back through the necklace for security. The necklace ties with satin machine-washable ribbon so you can adjust the length and you don't have to worry about broken clasps. When the ribbon gets dirty from general wear and tear, simply unloop it from the necklace, put it in a lingerie bag and throw in the wash along with your normal load. The ribbon ends are heat sealed so that it doesn't fray. 

Mumma Necklaces are for the fashion-conscious and safety-minded Mumma (or grandmother, aunty or early childhood professional!!) 

Mumma Necklaces are designed and personally road tested to survive the tugging and chewing of a curious baby. 

**Although every precaution has been made to make this a safe accessory for bubs to play with, adult supervision is still recommended. It is not a toy or teething device, and is not designed to be worn by a child.**

More Mumma Necklaces are available at www.thecoffeeapple.com.au
